  <summary>SQuirreL SQL Client is a graphical Java program (GUI) that will allow you to view the structure of a JDBC compliant database, browse the data in tables, issue SQL commands etc. The Flatpak version currently supports MySQL, PostgreSQL, MariaDB, and SQLite.</summary>
